  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (205°C).",
    "Rinse clams, remove any beards, and scrub shells under cold water.",
    "In a skillet, toast almonds over medium heat until golden brown. Let cool and roughly chop.",
    "Add garlic to the toasted almonds and sauté for 1 minute. Stir in red pepper flakes and salt and pepper.",
    "Place clams directly into the skillet with the almond mixture, cover, and bake for 8-10 minutes or until tender.",
    "Gently fold chopped parsley over clams before serving."
